                     <interp inst="t17820703-30-person329" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I was in the necessary, and knew nothing of it.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner called three witnesses, who gave him a good character.)</p>
